description._content: Bain News Service,, publisher. Mrs. F.W. Vanderbilt arriving, 8/14 1914 Aug. (date created or published later by Bain) 1 negative : glass ; 5 x 7 in. or smaller. Notes: Title and date from data provided by the Bain News Service on the negative. Photograph shows Louise Holmes Anthony Torrance (Mrs. Frederick W. Vanderbilt), wife of Frederick William Vanderbilt (1856-1938) on the ship Principe di Udine. (Source: Flickr Commons project, 2011) Forms part of: George Grantham Bain Collection (Library of Congress). Format: Glass negatives. Rights Info: No known restrictions on publication.
